      "role": "user",
      "content": "That makes sense, but it sounds a bit predatory. It feels like they've buried some really sneaky risks in there that aren't immediately obvious. Are there any specific \"hidden\" things in that wording that I should be looking for to protect myself?",
      "source": "evaluator"
